      <h1>HTML Basics</h1>
      <p>HTML uses simple tags to mark up content.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>Common Elements</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> for a main heading</li>
        <li><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> for a paragraph</li>
        <li><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> with <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> for a list</li>
        <li><code>&lt;img&gt;</code> for images with <code>alt</code> text</li>
        <li><code>&lt;a&gt;</code> for links</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

